Branded Buyer
Job Seekers
|
|
what:
where:
Singapore
International high-street fashion retailer is seeking a womenswear Branded Buyer to be based in their head office in Singapore.
This person will be tasked with building up relationships with key high-street fashion brands and then selecting the right collections for the various countries the business is present in across South East Asia.
You should be both trend-driven and commercially aware, with an excellent understanding of the words fashion industry.
You will be responsible for identifying key seasonal trends, whilst also having the skills to build strong and lasting partnerships with key international brands.
This individual needs to be both passionate and driven and have an understanding of the trends within the industry. This involves proactively conducting competitor analysis whilst also making recommendations on initiatives to continuously improve product ranging.
As the business continues to grow you will be responsible for growing your team so experience in hiring and training will also be beneficial.
We need someone that is entrepreneurial, passionate and creative.
This is an opportunity to work for in an international, professional and entrepreneurial business environment as well as the opportunity to be part of the development of a fast-growing and exciting fashion business.
